{
  "page": "Sea king",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Greyiron.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/250px-House_Greyiron.svg.png\" width=\"250\" height=\"275\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/375px-House_Greyiron.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/16/House_Greyiron.svg/500px-House_Greyiron.svg.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Greyiron.svg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The sigil of House Greyiron.</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>sea king</b> is a figure depicted on the arms of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\">House Greyiron</a>, according to a semi-canon source. He has dark green seaweed beard and hair.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The sea king may be related to the <a href=\"/index.php/Drowned_God\" title=\"Drowned God\">Drowned God</a>, since his <a href=\"/index.php/Priest_of_the_Drowned_God\" title=\"Priest of the Drowned God\">priests</a> use dried seaweed which they braid through their long hair and untrimmed beard.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sea_king&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/3/\">Heraldry - On the Iron Isles</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 11\">Chapter 11</a>, Theon I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404154547\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.016 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 136/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8570/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 409/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 867/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    9.321      1 -total\n 74.39%    6.934      1 Template:Ref\n 55.23%    5.148      1 Template:Ref/core\n 24.36%    2.271      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:38319-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404154547 and revision id 329313\n -->\n",
